channel.title: 667 Connects then disconnects
channel.description: I was trying to log in to my 667 server on my laptop and it would connect and then disconnect; I try on my pc and it connects. My friend could log on and then all of a sudden he keeps disconnecting a few seconds after he connects. Halp
